snippet.title: SPRINT VECTOR | Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
NOW AVAILABLE!:
Sprint Vector on PSVR: http://bit.ly/SprintVectorPSVR
Sprint Vector on Steam: http://bit.ly/SprintVectorOnSteam
Sprint Vector on Oculus Home: http://bit.ly/SprintVectorOnOculus
Official website: https://www.sprintvector.com

Welcome to Sprint Vector Championship Intergalactica, where media mastermind Mr. Entertainment has merged the physical thrill of extreme sports meets the unhinged energy of a zany game show! Run, jump, climb, drift, and fly at extreme velocity as you race up to 8 players and battle obstacles in this frenetic VR adrenaline platformer!
